statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_calibration_data;
SELECT experiment_id, calibration_date FROM quantum_calibration_data ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE device_id = 1;
SELECT experiment_id, calibration_values->>'offset' FROM quantum_calibration_data;
SELECT DISTINCT device_id FROM quantum_calibration_data ORDER BY device_id;
SELECT * FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE experiment_id = 1 ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, device_id, jsonb_extract_path_text(calibration_values, 'temperature') AS temperature FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE device_id = 2;
SELECT experiment_id, device_id, jsonb_extract_path(calibration_values, '{voltage, current}') AS voltage_current FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE calibration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT experiment_id, device_id, jsonb_array_elements(calibration_values -> 'results') AS calibration_results FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE device_id = 3;

SELECT AVG(jsonb_extract_path(calibration_values, 'temperature')) AS avg_temperature, MAX(jsonb_extract_path(calibration_values, 'pressure')) AS max_pressure FROM quantum_calibration_data WHERE device_id = 4;
